  "prompt": "Is T-fal cookware oven safe?",
  "response": "T-fal cookware is generally designed to be versatile and user-friendly, but whether it is oven safe depends on the specific product line. Many T-fal products, especially those with metal handles and oven-safe materials, can withstand oven temperatures. However, some non-stick coatings and plastic parts may not be suitable for high-heat environments.\n\nTo determine if a specific piece of T-fal cookware is oven safe, check the manufacturer's instructions or the product packaging. If in doubt, it's best to refer to the official T-fal website or customer service for detailed specifications regarding your particular cookware item.",
